 He worked at home.

Present progressive.

 He is working at home.

Past progressive. 

 He was working at home.

Present perfect.

 He has worked at home.

Past prefect.

 He had worked at home.

Present perfect progressive.

 He has been wokring at home.

Past perfect progressive.
 
 He had been working at home.


